Source.Contents:
/#
 Defines points in the day when equity option exercise and valuation can occur.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.TimeTypeEnum {
    # The official closing time of the exchange on the valuation date.
    Close 
    # The official opening time of the exchange on the valuation date.
    Open 
    # The time at which the official settlement price is determined.
    OSP 
    # The time specified in the element equityExpirationTime or valuationTime (as appropriate)
    SpecificTime 
    # The time at which the official settlement price (following the auction by the exchange) is determined by the exchange.
    XETRA 
    # The official closing time of the derivatives exchange on which a derivative contract is listed on that security underlyer.
    DerivativesClose 
    # The time is determined as provided in the relevant Master Confirmation.
    AsSpecifiedInMasterConfirmation 

}

Close.Doc: The official closing time of the exchange on the valuation date.
Close.Name: Close

Open.Doc: The official opening time of the exchange on the valuation date.
Open.Name: Open

OSP.Doc: The time at which the official settlement price is determined.
OSP.Name: OSP

SpecificTime.Doc: The time specified in the element equityExpirationTime or valuationTime (as appropriate)
SpecificTime.Name: SpecificTime

XETRA.Doc: The time at which the official settlement price (following the auction by the exchange) is determined by the exchange.
XETRA.Name: XETRA

DerivativesClose.Doc: The official closing time of the derivatives exchange on which a derivative contract is listed on that security underlyer.
DerivativesClose.Name: DerivativesClose

AsSpecifiedInMasterConfirmation.Doc: The time is determined as provided in the relevant Master Confirmation.
AsSpecifiedInMasterConfirmation.Name: AsSpecifiedInMasterConfirmation
